  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hospital Playground for Recovering Sick Children</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will begin the building of a children&apos;s playground area in one of Greece&apos;s main hospitals, the University Hospital in Heraklion, Crete.  Every year thousands of children from different countries receiving care will benefit physically and emotionally from a place to play together in the mild climate, especially those with respiratory diseases like Covid 19.  Playing is proven to help sick children overcome their illness, build strength and help them cope.</narrative>
  </description>
